dct_title_s: Map showing the surficial deposits of southeastern Wisconsin
dct_description_sm: by Wm. C. Alden ; base from Geological Survey topographic maps, data from General Land Office, and county maps and atlases.
Covers Wisconsin from the Illinois state line to Lake Winnebago.
